data.description: Check out the price reduction on this private oasis! Beautifully remodeled home on 6+ acres in Country Acres! Feel the seclusion when you enter the driveway, as no neighbors can be seen when the leaves are on the trees. 5 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms on the main and second levels, as well as a beautiful office. The kitchen has brand new appliances, and quartz counters. One half guest bathroom on the main level, along with a very spacious and private master bedroom. The large laundry room is plumbed for a mud sink. The basement is its own little suite, containing both a bedroom and bathroom, plus a kitchen! The deck can be accessed from the master bedroom and the living area. City utilities and no HOA!
